div(class="window_container")
  div(class="window_title")
  div(id="shopping_import" class="window_content portable_shopping_list")
    div(class="header")
      img(src="/public/images/tesco_logo.svg")
    div(class="section")
      p Quickly populate your shopping list by pulling in data from another supermarket. You've chosen to import data from the last time you shopped with Asda. 
      p Click below to import that data.
      a(id="import_shopping" class="chunky_button" href="#") Import from Asda
      
  div(id="shopping_list" class="window_content portable_shopping_list")
    div(class="header")
      img(src="/public/images/tesco_logo.svg")
    div(class="section")
      div(class="shopping")
      div(id="top_list")
        p Skimmed milk - 2 litres
          span £1.50
        p Kingsmill bread - loaf
          span £1.32
        p Bag of rice - 1kg
          span £1.22
        p Granny smith apples x5
          span £1.60
        p Fig roll biscuits
          span £40p
        p Mince meat - lean (500g)
          span £3.82
        p Smoked bacon
          span £1.74

      div(class="results")
        h2 Total cost
          span £11.60
        p Delivery tomorrow - 20:00
        a(id="checkout" class="chunky_button" href="#") Purchase

  div(id="shopping_accept" class="window_content portable_shopping_list")
    div(class="header")
      img(src="/public/images/tesco_logo.svg")
    div(class="section")
      h2 Your shopping is on it's way. 
      p Thank you for sharing your Asda shopping list with Tesco.  
            
